data.description: As you enter this 3 bedroom,2 bath home you will be greeted with an open concept, split bedroom plan.  Why wait for New Construction to finish being built when you can move into this home that was completed in 2022. This Home is nestled in the booming area of Lehigh Acres, right down the street from the new firehouse! This open concept home comes with designer cabinets and hardware, 18" tile through all living areas, all kitchen appliances including the garage fridge & latest Smart Home technology with a smart thermostat, smart door lock, video door bell,& more! The open kitchen concept is perfect for entertaining. All window and door curtains convey, TV in living area, wall shelf under TV, living room couch, master bed & dresser, toddler bed & dresser are all included in the sale. Agents- see remarks- Motivated sellers
